{"tid":267293,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"深水埗AVA 61迷你戶逾151呎起 (15:03)","createTime":"2017-06-02T07:36:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-02T08:58:35.000Z","uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"60f2c03b23688ccbcb3ead8c790427cb7c854bf5","tid":267293,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T07:36:07.000Z","msg":"資深投資者盧華旗下深水埗大埔道項目命名為AVA 61。維達創建項目策劃總監盧文德表示，項目提供130餘伙，一層設6伙，主打開放式及1房單位，最快第3季推售，預計2020年落成，「最細單位肯定不會細過151方呎」。項目地下及1樓設有8個商舖，每個約500方呎，傾向長線收租。<br />\n現時發展成AVA 61的地盤於去年11月透過強拍統一業權，成交價約2.67億元，總投資額逾4億元。集團過往推售的佐敦上海街AVA 62最細單位實用151方呎；另馬頭角AVA 55最細單位實用166方呎。至於西營盤AVA 128最近開始入伙，3個項目的住宅部份已套現約11億元。"},{"pid":"464e2d7fa723a231dfdca136ac9b7c10b30cba7b","tid":267293,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T07:43:07.000Z","msg":"又係呢類盤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c715fcd71e7975eeef581d20ddf17b2a9cb4243","tid":267293,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T07:44:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又係呢類盤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上車恩物，龍床首選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fed5c211f3eb2fa7f4cd48fd1b694c143cc6a34","tid":267293,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T07:45:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又係呢類盤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果係自住,就預左放唔出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"715803ba2b87b8f46a8b2753d7f2940789b809db","tid":267293,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T07:45:43.000Z","msg":"細過我間房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 相信唔會有人買黎自住掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但其實買完真係租得出咩？咁撚細 有人肯租？"},{"pid":"ec3094cfa8003dafdead9e4adf4c0f7058577506","tid":267293,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T07:54:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細過我間房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 相信唔會有人買黎自住掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但其實買完真係租得出咩？咁撚細 有人肯租？</blockquote><br />\n好過租天台屋"},{"pid":"48e066d8c0e96956cbc7f9090f3a04bb81fa05f2","tid":267293,"uid":38253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T08:29:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>細過我間房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 相信唔會有人買黎自住掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但其實買完真係租得出咩？咁撚細 有人肯租？</blockquote><br />\n好過租天台屋</blockquote><br />\n唔好講笑 呢類單位只會起得愈黎愈多<br />\n一黎真係有人會買 而且唔少 係市場既大趨勢<br />\n二黎呢類單位係最好賺 普遍單位愈細 呎價愈貴 而且發水發得最爽歪歪 <br />\n呃完你秤仲可以sell係上車盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63051713c7257b9336e0e0268ee2dd522f5a0b9f","tid":267293,"uid":112226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T08:58:35.000Z","msg":"正"}]}